channel.title: Disconnection problems?
channel.description: Well I shouldn't say it's disconnection problems but lemme explain :D. I go to my source and click run, then i go on silabsoft client and then I log in, the amount of time im able to be on before the DC is random. So when I do get DCD I try to log back in and it wont even load when i hit log in itll just say " your account is already on " as if it didnt log me out when I got DCD any1 know why? I compiled server and had no errors?
